<P><PB N="215" REF="216">
We will leave this re&s;pectable <HI>court of
$laims,</HI> to examine the charge now prepar|ing
by Lady Bla&s;t again&s;t Mi&s;s Villiers, to
&s;ettle our heroine's preten&s;ions to continue
